item.title: Getting Started
item.description: Proter is available as a library from Maven Central, so you can add it as a dependency in your project. For example, in sbt: 1libraryDependencies += "com.workflowfm" %% "proter" % "0.7.1" Proter is currently only available in Scala 2.12.12.
